articles.title: Pope sparks anger after saying Ukraine should have the ‘courage of the white flag’ and negotiate - CNN
articles.description: Ukrainian and European officials slammed over the weekend comments by Pope Francis, who in an interview published Saturday had said Kyiv should negotiate with Russia to end the fighting.
articles.content:
Pope Francis has sparked anger after saying Ukraine should have the courage of the white flag and negotiate to end the war with Russia.
